OL,3,CThe Cuban Exodus: Hospital workers,
OL,4,Ctourists, young people fleeing the
OL,5,Ccountry
OL,7,FAdditional reporting by Washington
OL,8,FNews Editor Jonathan Wald
OL,10,FDr Eugenio Selman is a man on a
OL,11,Fmission.
OL,13,FHe is a passionate, tactile surgeon
OL,14,Fwho grips my arm as he explains the
OL,15,Fplight of his hospital, Cardiocentro
OL,16,FPediatrico William Soler, the only
OL,17,Fspecialist heart hospital for children
OL,18,Fin Cuba.
OL,20,FIt must operate with less than half of
OL,21,Fits normal staff.
OL,26,@xD@Erp
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1781308974
OL,3,CThe Cuban Exodus: Hospital workers,
OL,4,Ctourists, young people fleeing the
OL,5,Ccountry
OL,7,FFaced with economic hardship that
OL,8,Fworsens daily, some have left for
OL,9,Fbetter-paid jobs elsewhere, some are
OL,10,Funable to travel to work because of a
OL,11,Flack of fuel, and others have decided
OL,12,Fto leave Cuba altogether.
OL,14,FIt means Selman and the remaining
OL,15,Fdoctors and nurses are struggling to
OL,16,Fhelp the children who have severe
OL,17,Fheart conditions.
OL,19,FSome wards are closed because there is
OL,20,Fno one to run them.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1781308974
OL,3,CThe Cuban Exodus: Hospital workers,
OL,4,Ctourists, young people fleeing the
OL,5,Ccountry
OL,7,FYears ago, this hospital was one of
OL,8,Fthe jewels of Castro's health system
OL,9,Fand had no waiting list.
OL,11,FNow some 700 children are holding out
OL,12,Ffor operations, facing months of
OL,13,Fdelays, discomfort and risk.
OL,15,FDr Selman blames the US blockade for
OL,16,Fthe deteriorating situation.
OL,18,FThe Americans insist they have not
OL,19,Fblockaded medicines.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1781308974
OL,3,CThe Cuban Exodus: Hospital workers,
OL,4,Ctourists, young people fleeing the
OL,5,Ccountry
OL,7,FAn American official told ITV News
OL,8,Fthat "medicines are and have always
OL,9,Fbeen exempted".
OL,11,F"The regime's failed policies and
OL,12,Fcorrupt leadership have caused the
OL,13,FCuban people immense hardship," the
OL,14,Fofficial went on to say.
OL,16,F"Regime leaders squirrel away billions
OL,17,Fin foreign accounts while everyday
OL,18,FCubans go hungry and without medicine."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1781308974
OL,3,CThe Cuban Exodus: Hospital workers,
OL,4,Ctourists, young people fleeing the
OL,5,Ccountry
OL,7,FBut Dr Selman claims obtaining
OL,8,Fequipment like catheters, specialist
OL,9,Fantibiotics to treat infection like
OL,10,Fthe drug Amphotericin, or drugs like
OL,11,FAdenosine, used to treat the heart
OL,12,Fcondition, arrhythmia, are fraught
OL,13,Fwith red tape and delays.
OL,15,FHe also fears companies that may be
OL,16,Ftechnically permitted to provide
OL,17,Fmedicine and resources are intimidated
OL,18,Fby the potential loss of business with
OL,19,Fthe US if they are seen to be trading
OL,20,Fwith Cuba.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1781308974
OL,3,CThe Cuban Exodus: Hospital workers,
OL,4,Ctourists, young people fleeing the
OL,5,Ccountry
OL,7,FWhile that is part of the story, so
OL,8,Ftoo is the exodus of skilled staff
OL,9,Ffrom this country.
OL,11,FSome 800,000 Cubans are currently
OL,12,Fapplying for Spanish citizenship in
OL,13,Forder to leave the country.
OL,15,FThat represents almost 10% of the
OL,16,Fapproximately 10 million population.
OL,18,F"El ley de nietos" or the "Law of
OL,19,FGrandchildren" enables anyone who can
OL,20,Fprove they have a grandparent to apply
OL,21,Ffor citizenship.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1781308974
OL,3,CThe Cuban Exodus: Hospital workers,
OL,4,Ctourists, young people fleeing the
OL,5,Ccountry
OL,7,FEach day, dozens line up outside the
OL,8,Foffice where applications are
OL,9,Fprocessed.
OL,11,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,12,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,13,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,14,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,16,FAmong them is Jonathan Adaj, who
OL,17,Finstalls solar panels.
OL,19,FHis sister is about to receive her
OL,20,FSpanish passport, and he's hoping he
OL,21,Fwill be next.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1781308974
OL,3,CThe Cuban Exodus: Hospital workers,
OL,4,Ctourists, young people fleeing the
OL,5,Ccountry
OL,7,FHe has plans to move to Madrid if he
OL,8,Fis successful, taking his much-needed
OL,9,Fskills with him.
OL,11,FIn a country with crippling shortages
OL,12,Fof electricity, solar panels could
OL,13,Foffer some relief for struggling
OL,14,Fbusinesses, but Jonathan's departure
OL,15,Fis emblematic of the problems Cuba's
OL,16,Fgovernment is facing.
OL,18,FWe visited Envametal, a factory where
OL,19,Fa solar system has been installed to
OL,20,Fpower the administrative offices.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1781308974
OL,3,CThe Cuban Exodus: Hospital workers,
OL,4,Ctourists, young people fleeing the
OL,5,Ccountry
OL,7,FWhile we were visiting, there was a
OL,8,Fpower cut, but their computers and
OL,9,Flights remained operational due to the
OL,10,Fnew panels on the roof.
OL,12,FBut it cannot provide enough for the
OL,13,Ffactory itself, which manufactures
OL,14,Faluminium and tin products.
OL,16,FAfter the power does not come back on
OL,17,Ffor two hours, the workers are sent
OL,18,Fhome for the day.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
